    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that still turns heads? I\u2019m parting with this beauty, and it\u2019s in really solid shape! It runs like a dream and has been super well-maintained. It\u2019s perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. I\u2019ve loved driving this car, and I know you will too. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 32500.0,
