    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted E46 M3, featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine characterized by its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM ceiling. This unit is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering torque through a variable M differential lock. Significant preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a VANOS system refresh and a comprehensive subframe reinforcement to maintain structural integrity under high lateral loads. The suspension utilizes a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup, with bushings recently inspected to ensure the chassis remains communicative. While the aesthetic reflects its status as a driven machine, the powertrain remains tight and the hydraulic steering rack provides the unfiltered feedback enthusiasts demand. A robust example of analog performance engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Well-maintained. Clean interior. Ready for immediate use.",
