      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving 4.0L S65 naturally aspirated V8. This unit delivers a linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline, breathing through eight individual throttle bodies. The six-speed longitudinal manual transmission provides tactile engagement, sending power through a Variable M Differential Lock. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including the replacement of rod bearings and throttle actuators. The chassis retains its composure via Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and remains stiff under lateral load. While the Interlagos Blue finish shows minor road rash consistent with enthusiast use, the mechanical synchrony between the VANOS system and the valvetrain is impeccable. It currently sits on staggered forged Style 220M alloys wrapped in fresh rubber, ready for the apex.",
